                <h2>14 Oct 2012, 7:30 p.m.</h2>

                <p>Bresson’s second feature and his last using professional actors.It’s a devilish take on the love triangle theme. Wonderfully scripted by Jean Cocteau, sexuality takes precedence over salvation.</p>

